jcr:content.jcr:title: 46th Annual Houston Fiesta Patrias International Parade

data.details: All Girl Scouts of San Jacinto Council are invited to participate in the 46th annual Houston Fiestas Patrias International Parade! This is a fantastic opportunity for girls to represent their troop and Girl Scout pride while celebrating the generations of Hispanic Americans who have positively influenced and enriched our nation and society. To register, contact Laura Covarrubias at 713-292-0354 or lcovarrubias@sjgs.org.
data.srchdisp: For more information contact the Emerging Markets Director at 713-292-0300.
